Name: ProjectID
Notes:
Must match a ProjectID in Project.csv where
(ProjectType = 6) or (ProjectType = 13 and
RRHSubType = 1)

Name: ResProjectID
Notes:
Must match a record in Project.csv where
ProjectType = 1,2, 3, 8, 10, or 13. If ProjectType =
13, RRHSubType must be 2.

Name: ExportID
Notes: Must match the ExportID in Export.csv
